---
title: Slurp's Up! Sesame Chicken Noodles with Crunchy Cabbage and a Chilli Oil Drizzle
description: Looking to ride a wave of sesame? Then this recipe is sure to float your boat. These fun and far out noodles are coated in a sauce that has an unexpected (but delicious) combo of spicy and sweet. Also along for the ride are wisps of crunchy cabbage, a spike of fiery chili oil, and chicken pieces that will have you shredding it, literally.
